card.name: CW - CCW256 - Link to the admins data for extracts

data.text:
@cobuspienaar @yasserogier 
All admin orders are captured on credit's servers. Compuscan gets the data from credit's ftp. we needed to get the data through a web service and inject them into the normal files for TU, XDS and EX. That injection is not working currently or possibly the data is not coming through the service.
